      "body": "> Another option is to drop support for fork runs. I personally find this to be an annoyance in general and don't see why we should support it with so much spaghetti in ci.yml. But I would open a discussion before proposing that.\r\n\r\nSeems fine, too. Though, it would be nice to have a one-line (?) scripted diff to still support that somewhat. E.g. `sed --regexp-extended --in-place 's/warp-(ubuntu-([^-]+))-x64-.x/\\1/g' .github/workflows/ci.yml`",
